OL,3,CMillie Bobby Brown calls girl left
OL,4,Corphaned after crash
OL,6,FA girl who was left orphaned when the
OL,7,Frest of her family were killed in a
OL,8,Fcar crash has been consoled by her
OL,9,FHollywood idol Millie Bobby Brown.
OL,11,FThe Stranger Things and Godzilla
OL,12,Factress called 11-year-old Poppie
OL,13,FRoller on Tuesday after hearing about
OL,14,Fthe tragedy earlier this month.
OL,16,FWriting online on Wednesday, family
OL,17,Ffriend Paul Hepple said: "Yesterday,
OL,18,FPoppie and her best friend had a video
OL,19,Fcall with Millie Bobby Brown!
