OL,3,CMillie Bobby Brown calls girl left
OL,4,Corphaned after crash
OL,6,F"Millie was absolutely amazing and
OL,7,Fsuper supportive.
OL,9,F"While the girls were a bit shy during
OL,10,Fthe call, they went absolutely crazy
OL,11,Fwith excitement afterward and couldn't
OL,12,Fstop talking about Millie and the
OL,13,Fwonderful experience."
OL,15,FThe call "put a huge smile" on
OL,16,FPoppie's face during a "challenging"
OL,17,Ftime, he said.
