OL,3,CMillie Bobby Brown calls girl left
OL,4,Corphaned after crash
OL,6,FPoppie lost her parents, Shannen
OL,7,FMorgan and Shane Roller, and her
OL,8,Fsisters Rubie and Lillie when their
OL,9,Fcar was involved in a collision with a
OL,10,Fmotorbike on the A61 between Wakefield
OL,11,Fand Barnsley on 21 July.
OL,13,FChristopher and Janine Barton, a
OL,14,Fmarried couple who were on the bike,
OL,15,Falso died.
OL,17,FA man arrested on suspicion of causing
OL,18,Fdeath by dangerous driving remains on
OL,19,Fbail.
