OL,3,CMillie Bobby Brown calls girl left
OL,4,Corphaned after crash
OL,6,FFollowing the tragedy, Mr Hepple set
OL,7,Fup a fundraiser to support Poppie. It
OL,8,Fhas now raised almost #400,000.
OL,10,FHe said Poppie's aunt, who is now
OL,11,Fcaring for her, is due to meet a
OL,12,Ffinancial advisor to discuss how the
OL,13,Fmoney is used.
OL,15,FMr Hepple said: "We are committed to
OL,16,Fhandling the donations responsibly,
OL,17,Fwith all funds going directly towards
OL,18,FPoppie's wellbeing and future.
