OL,6,F"We appreciate all the advice and
OL,7,Fconcerns shared about setting up a
OL,8,Ftrust fund, and we want to reassure
OL,9,Feveryone that the funds will be
OL,10,Fsafeguarded for Poppie's needs."
OL,12,FHe added: "Together, we are making a
OL,13,Fsignificant positive impact on
OL,14,FPoppie's life."
